Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Full-Stack Software Development Engineer position with Texas Instruments. I bring over three years of professional experience in full-stack web applications, AI code generation platforms, and agentic frameworks, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

